{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbb13c913-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1443"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1443"},"text":"§ 1443.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Provisions as controlling over other laws","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Insofar as the provisions of any other law are inconsistent with the provisions of this Act, the provisions of this Act shall be controlling.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbb13c914-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-07-15/ch338"},"text":"July 15, 1949, ch. 338","children":[],"tail":", title VI, § 610, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/443"},"text":"63 Stat. 443","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbb13c915-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbb13c916-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbb13c917-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1949-07-15/ch338"},"text":"act July 15, 1949, ch. 338","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/63/413"},"text":"63 Stat. 413","children":[],"tail":", known as the Housing Act of 1949, which is classified principally to this chapter (§ 1441 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Cod